，比箭更准还更快。」 对洛恩而言，武器和战术没有孰强孰弱，只有效率高低。当放冷箭就放箭，该上枪时就上枪。尽管用枪尖刺穿甲衣的手感最是令人愉悦，但若是为了更高效的胜利，设伏下毒奇袭潜入也不失为好手段。 只不过在他需要放冷箭的时候，往往不会留下什么目击者。 也因如此，他给人留下的印象，总是战场上那一抹执锐疾驰的迅影。 像破空而至的利箭与枪弹，却更是狠厉，也更不容躲闪。 关注 @原神 并转发，我们将随机抽选 10 位旅行者赠送【原神随机周边】 1 份。 本次活动将于 4 月 21 日 14:00 开奖，请关注官方消息。请旅行者于开奖后 15 日内提交获奖信息（逾期视为自动放弃奖励）。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-579e58ba789c0114a74238505f10c92b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "108 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2027366408900682424"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI7d7G4qL277csEAMaCTExOTEzODMwMyD6i/fOBjAAOB5AEHITMjAyNzM2NjQwODkwMDY4MjQyNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1776220489.438592", "card_id": "Q_2022261313766793653", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《洛克王国：世界》 目前内容有些贫瘠，应该增加什么内容才能长久运营？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-bb95d2943632231907d320282a31c2e0.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "92 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022261313766793653"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI7d7G4qL277csEAMaCTExODk2NTg2MCD95qzOBjAAOBJAEXITMjAyMjI2MTMxMzc2Njc5MzY1M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1776220489.438922", "card_id": "Q_2025694493131719186", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "运动员没练出来的话，生活是怎么样的呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[2 张图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8df22fada03d06